    "body": "It seems that the vulnerability can't be triggered from `slog-scope` (and therefore Lighthouse). It effects `arc_swap::access::Map`, which is unused by `slog-scope`. It seems `slog-scope` only uses the most basic features of `arc-swap`, see:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/slog-rs/scope/blob/7c93a607ebf14567840331228da0a7f19d1fcfa5/lib.rs\r\n\r\nThis means the v1.0.4 release is viable.",
